title: 01 = Zero one. [Ep. 73/02]
brief_description: Cinemagazine items including: 1. Poison research and cures. 2. Launching ship for carrying barges for steel cargo and containers. 3. Aerodynamics of the helicopter. 4. Inflatable jack to move objects without damage, and inflatable tent. 5. Music reproduction via machines in early years of 20th century.
